 the trail is technical with plenty of hills, log hops, and turns - AWESOME riding. The trail system is accessible any time - if you don&#39;t know where to go, check out the map of the Quarry Trails on www.fambe.org.

 Beginners: 1 SMALL loop &#x28;~6miles&#x29;

Experts: 2 BIG loops &#x28;18 miles&#x29;

All others: 1 BIG and 1 SMALLER loop &#x28;13 miles&#x29;
